      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained by its previous owners. Mechanically, it is very reliable, featuring an engine that starts reliably and a transmission that shifts smoothly through all gears. While there may be some minor cosmetic wear consistent with its age, the interior remains clean and the overall structure is sound. Buyers can expect a dependable car that is ready for daily use without needing immediate major repairs.",
