    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking for a new home for this absolute gem of a ride. It has been incredibly reliable for me and is still in wonderful shape, both inside and out! It's super comfortable, looks great on the road, and is totally ready for your next adventure. I've taken really good care of it, and I'm sure you're going to love how it drives. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look\u2014I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
